commit.message: added hero card views for memes in chat
Fixed the tweet picture urls not working
Switched from a hard-coded city to grabbing tweets for each city
Updated the radius to check tweets to 100 miles from 500 miles
The timestamp for each tweet is now grabbed and passed to the database along with all the other information.
The script grabs tweet data including the image url, likescount, repliescount, and retweetscount. The data is written to the database. Tweets are found for cities listed in the database.
The basic twitter scraping works now
